<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The priest (shows up like a ghoul btw), was red to me at 29, but I still had no trouble blasting the hell out of him with my 34 warrior friend assisting (Wizard here).  The sonofabitch is a healer though, so try stunning him when he gets low.  The spawn is sort of random, anywhere from 45min to 1hr 45min.  Also, periodically skellies and carrion ghouls come by to harass you (all blue to me).<BR>
I hope this helps, good luck all.<BR>
<BR>
Sibige Londeir of the Kindred Spirits of Tarew Marr<BR>
-only camped the bastard for 6 hours, luckier than anyone else I've heard from on my server.<BR>
