<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: slick chanter</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-26 01:04:55</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>i was leveling in unrest one day and i see a group (in wolf form) RUNNING to the other end of the house.<BR>
<BR>
at first i thought it was a tarin so i invised undead but nothing was coming so i was curious and followed, turns out the druid had seen the priest on track, the priest was much to high level for the party (much to high for me also even though i was a good 4 or 5 levels higher then anyone in their group) so they attempt to kill it anyway, and it is almost dead 4 of their members are dead and the warrior and cleric are whats left it is down to a fraction of health and the cleric is oom, warrior about dead BUT it looks like they will win....<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
BLAM mem blur, nuke,gate as a train of ghouls come wipe out the cleric and warrior. woot xp for a red mob and no drop key, few hours later MYSTIC CLOAK!<BR>
<BR>
sometimes its GREAT to be an ASSHOLE hahahahaha.</font></td></tr></table>
