<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Albonez</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-30 22:59:33</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I just completed this quest.<BR>
This is how I did it so all you DE Necros out there go and get your cloaks!!<BR>
After I got the key from the priest I went and bound myself outside of felweth.I then got a tp to lavastorm.<BR>
After I got inside najena I conned the highelf she scowled at me no suprise. I then decided to go invis and hand it to her through the bars.I decided to practice first with a jailer key,as soon as I handed her the key my invis dropped before I could press give she attacked it is too late at this point.<BR>
OK next I decided to try skeleton form and she glowered at me threatingly.I thought with the invis and the skelly form it would work.IT DID! I positioned her body directly over where the trade screen pops up so that the exact moment I handed it to her the screen would pop up and the give button would be under my cursor and I could press it FAST. THIS WORKED!<BR>
At this point I was pumped up,but not to happy about going inside the highelf city.<BR>
I found her father behind the bank alone besides floating guard. I swam across the water behind him and found a place to skelly form and invis.I then came back and did the same steps as above.IT Worked! <BR>
He said "Thank you for saving my daughter,Dark Elves like you MUST DIE!"(if he thanks you the cloak will fly into your inventory) at this point I ran and feigned death near where I invised earlier,waited a few min stood up and gated.<BR>
<BR>
Now at this point wearing the worn cloak I am really pumped auctioning for a tp to eurdin where I have a feeling I am going to die(the mother is two zones in eurdin in the middle of the enchanter guild,not a safe place for de necros).After not very long I got a druid to tp me to eurdin. The druid asked me why I was going there and I explained about the cloak. The druid said I gotta see this!<BR>
So the druid and I went all the way to where her mother is at this point I tell the druid to mem an evac spell because I knew after I tried this things were going to BLOW UP!<BR>
I positioned myself just as before in skelly form and invised to the right of the mother hit both buttons and BAM I saw the cloak fly into my 1st slot(keep the first main inventory slot open)at that point she began to cast and all around me people began to cast I had just enough time to notice that the druid was casting also and BAM we evaced out to south ro unscathed with my awesome MYSTIC CLOAK!<BR>
I am posting this so my other dark elven brothers and sisters can get their cloaks so get busy!<BR>
as a side note it will make this quest easier if you have the circlet of shadows dropped in droga this allows for instant invis when right clicked.without it I would have completed the quest but I would have died a few times in the process.<BR>
Albonez Zal'Honan<BR>
Dark Elf Necromancer<BR>
XEGONY<BR>
Feel free to come and inspect me if anyone questions this.</font></td></tr></table>
