<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hi guys.  :-)  I am a lvl 49 enchanter and I have helped many necromancers get this cloak.  It isn't all that easy, and somewhat risky, but talk an enchanter friend of yours into charming the npc for that part of the quest.  He then becomes indifferent to you and you can do business with him.  Works like a "charm" cringes.  *hint*  same thing works for jboots if Hasten Bootstrutter doesn't like ya.<BR>
Peace and best of luck.</font></td></tr></table>
